c: 34
v: 43
t: "Si Aayeeje Amen …ďanngu…óe …óen janngaamma e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe wi'a: \"Oo wonaali, si wanaa gorko faalaa…óo falagol on e ko baabiraa…ďe mon rewayno rewaynoo\". ∆Āe wi'i: \"Ndee (Alqur‚Äôaanaare) wonaali, si wanaa fenaande fefindaande\". Yeddu…ďe …ďen wi'ani goonga kan nde ka arunoo e ma…ď…ďe: \"Ndee wonaali, si wanaa mbilewu …ďanngu ngu"